nodes.text: Oln Pressig was a male who served the Imperial Remnant around 43 ABY. Achieving the rank of Lieutenant, Pressig became Imperial Head of State Jagged Fel's day-shift Security Chief. However, in 43.5 ABY, Pressig came into league with the Senator of Kuat, Haydnat Treen, who used him to set forth her plot to unseat Fel, unite the Galactic Alliance with the Empire, and then unseat Galactic Alliance Chief of State Natasi Daala and become Empress of the galaxy. Pressig headed an attack with several other stormtroopers in an attempt to kidnap Fel in the Head of State's quarters in the Galactic Empire Embassy on Coruscant. However, Fel managed to fight off the troopers, killing six of them, including Pressig.
